    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
                
<p>Basically I'm trying to sort a complex array of Objects within an array:  </p>

<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">Array</span>
(
    [<span class="hljs-number">190515</span>] =&gt; <span class="hljs-built_in">stdClass</span> <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">Object</span>
        (
            [nid] =&gt; <span class="hljs-number">15740686</span>
            [venue_nid] =&gt; <span class="hljs-number">190515</span>
            [occurrences] =&gt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>
            [this_weeks_occurrences] =&gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>
            [end_date] =&gt; <span class="hljs-number">1350853200</span>
            [end_date_end_time] =&gt; <span class="hljs-number">1350853200</span>
            [is_ongoing] =&gt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>
            [title] =&gt; Wentz Concert Hall <span class="hljs-keyword">and</span> Fine Arts Center
            [times] =&gt; <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">Array</span>
                (
                    [<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] =&gt; <span class="hljs-built_in">stdClass</span> <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">Object</span>
