<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
        <div class="js-endorsements" data-for-answer="12753701">
</div>

    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>How about:</p>

<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">compare</span>(<span class="hljs-params"><span class="hljs-variable">$x</span>,<span class="hljs-variable">$y</span></span>)
</span>{
    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$x</span>-&gt;times[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]-&gt;occurrence_date == <span class="hljs-variable">$y</span>-&gt;times[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]-&gt;occurrence_date)
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">elseif</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$x</span>-&gt;times[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]-&gt;occurrence_date &lt; <span class="hljs-variable">$y</span>-&gt;times[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]-&gt;occurrence_date)
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> -<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;
    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>
        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;

}

<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">uasort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$your_array</span>,<span class="hljs-string">'compare'</span>);
</code></pre>

<p>uasort() preserve your keys, unlike usort()
<a href="http://www.php.net/manual/en/function.uasort.php" rel="nofollow">http://www.php.net/manual/en/function.uasort.php</a></p>
    </div>
